headline: Luckie Names Scott Gelber Chief Executive Officer to Lead Next Phase of Agency's Growth
summary: Marketing agency Luckie announced today that Scott Gelber is the company's new Chief Executive Officer, marking a key leadership transition as the firm looks to accelerate growth across the Southeast.

headline: Does Omnicom’s Recent Share Price Drop Present a New Opportunity for Investors in 2025?
summary: Thinking about what to do with Omnicom Group stock? You are not alone. After all, when a company that sits at the heart of global marketing communications trades at its lowest levels in years, it is bound to catch the attention of both cautious and opportunistic investors. Omnicom shares recently closed at $77.61, down 10.2% since the start of the year and more than 20% underwater compared to twelve months ago. On the surface, that might look like a warning sign.
